      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "The affected product lacks a function to check integrity and authenticity of uploaded logic, which could allow an attacker to execute malicious code on the device.CVE-2022-31800 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 9.8 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H).",
